RSU 13 bus driver arrested, charged in connection to crash that killed 12-year-old student
===

Jeffrey Colburn of Camden faces a manslaughter charge, according to Rockland police.

![](https://media.newscentermaine.com/assets/NCM/images/931c0b96-545a-48c4-84a2-e348471a6368/20251205T171757/931c0b96-545a-48c4-84a2-e348471a6368_16x9.jpg) ![](https://media.newscentermaine.com/assets/NCM/images/931c0b96-545a-48c4-84a2-e348471a6368/20251205T171757/931c0b96-545a-48c4-84a2-e348471a6368_750x422.jpg)

